<p>The Nobody's War hitmaker said: 'I never got to speak to her about it. Life goes on and obviously, we never crossed paths again. I was so sad to hear that news, man...It's so crazy that she passed away. It blows me away. I can't even believe it' </p>

<p>Her final screen role - as Cassie - alongside Dame Judi Dench in Jules Williamson's European train-set dramedy Off the Rails is currently in post-production.</p>

<p>Preston is survived by her 20-year-old daughter Ella Bleu and nine-year-old son Benjamin from her 29-year marriage to two-time Oscar nominee John Travolta.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, Adam has two daughters - Dusty Rose, turning 4 next Monday; and Gio Grace, 2 - from his six-year marriage to South African model Behati Prinsloo.</p>

<p>Levine's interview came two months after his LA band's bass player Mickey Madden announced he was 'taking leave of absence' after being arrested June 27 on domestic violence charges.</p>

